"配角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/70/c9/4785_prsn_ZqXwi.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/70/c9/4785_prsn_ZqXwi.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/70/c9/4785_prsn_ZqXwi.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/70/c9/4785_prsn_ZqXwi.jpg"},"name":"木村はるか","short_summary":"日本の女性声優、劇作家、脚本家。神奈川県出身。声優としてはヘリンボーン所属。以前はプロ・フィットに所属していた。血液型はA型。\r\n舞台脚本・演出家（劇作家）および脚本家としてのペンネームは森 悠。\r\n\r\nプロ・フィット第1期生。2012年6月のブログ上で声優業10周年と明かした。\r\n声優業の傍ら、脚本家として、森悠名義を用いて、劇団「クロジ」（乙女企画クロジ☆）の戯曲を執筆し、TVアニメ『断裁分離のクライムエッジ』『放課後のプレアデス』のシナリオにも参加している。\r\n趣味は読書とハンドメイド、得意なスポーツは水泳、特技はピアノの弾き語りと物真似。\r\n2014年12月5日にブログの報告で齋藤陽介と入籍した。","career":["producer","seiyu"],"id":4785,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":200528}],"detail":[{"birth_mon":null,"gender":"female","birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/10/ae/197005_crt_A3Jb5.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/10/ae/197005_crt_A3Jb5.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/10/ae/197005_crt_A3Jb5.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/10/ae/197005_crt_A3Jb5.jpg"},"summary":"","name":"オルガ","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"奥尔加"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"k":"英文名","v":"Olga"}]},{"key":"性别","value":"女"}],"stat":{"comments":0,"collects":0},"id":197005,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":null,"gender":"male","birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/fa/6d/199866_crt_x7Kgo.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/fa/6d/199866_crt_x7Kgo.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/fa/6d/199866_crt_x7Kgo.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/fa/6d/199866_crt_x7Kgo.jpg"},"summary":"","name":"テオ","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"提欧"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"k":"英文名","v":"Theo"}]},{"key":"性别","value":"男"}],"stat":{"comments":0,"collects":0},"id":199866,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":null,"gender":"male","birth_d